{{Other uses|Mono language (disambiguation)}}{{Infobox language |name=Mono |nativename= |states=[[Cameroon]] |ethnicity= |speakers=300 Mono |date=2001 |ref=e15 |speakers2=50 Dama (older adults, no date)<ref name=e15/> |familycolor=Niger-Congo |fam2=[[Atlantic–Congo languages|Atlantic–Congo]] |fam3=[[Mbum–Day languages|Mbum–Day]] |fam4=[[Mbum languages|Mbum]] |fam5=Northern Mbum |fam6=Dama–Galke |lc1=mru |ld1=Mono |lc2=dmm |ld2=Dama |glotto=mono1269 |glottoname=Mono |glotto2=dama1267 |glottoname2=Dama }}
'''Mono''' is a moribund [[Mbum languages|Mbum]] language spoken by older adults in northern [[Cameroon]]. A probable dialect, Dama, may already be extinct.
