{{Infobox writer | name = Ruswa Majhalumi | honorific_prefix = | honorific_suffix = | image = Poet Ruswa Majhalumi.jpg | caption = Poet Ruswa Majhalumi | native_name = બાબી ઈમામુદ્દીનખાન મુર્તઝાખાન | native_name_lang = guj | pseudonym = Ruswa Majhalumi | birth_name = Babi Imamuddinkhan Murtazakhan | birth_date = {{birth date|df=y|1915|12|11}}<ref name= "rm">{{cite encyclopedia |last=Vyas |first=Rajesh |author-link=Rajesh Vyas |editor-last=Topiwala |editor-first=Chandrakant |editor-link=Chandrakant Topiwala |encyclopedia=Gujarati Sahityakosh (Encyclopedia of Gujarati Literature) |title=Babi Imamuddin Murtazakhan |language= Gujarati |year=1990 |publisher=[[Gujarati Sahitya Parishad]] |volume=2 |location=Ahmedabad |pages=390}}</ref> | birth_place = [[Mangrol, Kathiawar|Mangrol]], [[Gujarat]]<ref name= "rm"/> | death_date ={{Death date and age|2008|2|14|1915|12|11|df=yes}} | death_place = <!---[[Vadodara]], Gujarat, India---> | resting_place = | occupation = Poet | language = [[Gujarati language|Gujarati]] | nationality = [[India]]n | education = | alma_mater = [[Rajkumar College, Rajkot]] | period = | genres = [[Ghazal]] | subjects = | movement = | notableworks = * ''Madira'' (1972) * ''Meena'' (1948) | spouse = | children = | relatives = | awards = | signature = | years_active = }}
'''Babi Imamuddinkhan Murtazakhan''' ([[Gujarati language|Gujarati]]: બાબી ઈમામુદ્દીનખાન મુર્તઝાખાન), batter known by his pen name '''Ruswa Majhalumi''' (Gujarati: રુસ્વા મઝલૂમી), was a Gujarati language poet and a royal of Pajod state. He was born in [[Mangrol, Kathiawar|Mangrol]] on 11 December 1915. He studied at [[Rajkumar College, Rajkot]] from 1927 to 1934.<ref name="Rajkumar College Rajkot Alumni">{{cite web | title=Mr. Ayaazkhan Babi | website=Rajkumar College Rajkot Alumni | url=http://rkcalumni.com/blog/mr-ayazkhan-babi/ | accessdate=2016-07-29}}</ref> ''Meena'' (1948) and ''Madira'' (1972) are two of his collection of [[Ghazal]] poetry. ''Dhalta Minara'' (1978) is an episodic portraits by him.<ref name= "rm"/>
He died on 14 February 2008.<ref>{{cite journal|title=Ruswa Majhalumi|journal=Shahid-e-Gazal|editor=Shakeel Qadri|issue=March–May|year=2008}}</ref>
He belonged to [[Babi Dynasty]].
