{{infobox language |name=Truká |nativename= |states=[[Brazil]] |region=[[Pernambuco]], [[Bahia]] |ethnicity= |extinct=? |familycolor=American |family=(unattested) |iso3=tka |glotto=truk1242 |glottorefname=Truká }}
'''Truká ''' is an [[extinct language|extinct]] and unattested, but presumed, language of [[Brazil]]. The ethnic population is about 1,300.
