{{Infobox language |name=Yanda |nativename=''Yanda Dom'' |region=[[Mali]] |speakers=2,000 |date=2005 |ref=e18 |familycolor=Niger-Congo |fam2=[[Dogon languages|Dogon]] |fam3=Nanga? |iso3=dym |glotto=yand1257 |glottorefname=Yanda Dom Dogon }} {{infobox ethnonym||Yanda Bɔlɔm||Yanda Dom}} '''Yanda Dogon''' is a [[Dogon language]] spoken in [[Mali]]. It is reported to be lexically similar to [[Nanga Dogon|Nanga]], which is only known from one report from 1953.
